## What this session delivered

### 1. Clippy fix (1 file)
- `crates/afa-kernel/tests/llm_integration.rs` lines 298-299:
  `assert_eq!(req_evt.has_tools, false)` →
  `assert!(!req_evt.has_tools)` (and same for `has_images`).
  The `bool_assert_comparison` lint is `-D warnings` so it was
  a hard error.

### 2. Doc patch (1 file)
- `docs/plugins/LlmHttp.md`: clarified the plugin targets the
