## Key design decisions locked in this session

None — Phase 4 is integration + CI + documentation, not new
design. All design decisions are unchanged from Phases 0–3
(see the previous handoffs for the full design lock list:
LlmV1 stateless, `describe_capabilities` sync, 3-step key
wiring, raw reqwest SSE in both sibling crates, the
multi-turn fold-into-`complete` pattern, the streaming
tool-call contract, the 13 LlmErrorV1 variants).

